data.name: /whois

description: With hundreds of new gTLDs in the wild and even more on the horizon the days of everyone rolling their own WHOIS data parser are over. JsonWHOISAPI frees you from the countless hours it takes to build and maintain separate parser for each gTLD. Our Parsed WHOIS data is available through a completely un-throttled REST API and if you encounter any issues with our service we offer fanatical developer and sales support as standard with each account. Sign-up today for a free account, no credit card needed!
